data.description: **Open House Sunday 12/17 11am-1pm** Back on market, here's your chance! Are you looking for a 4-bedroom home in the Bethany area that has a bigger than a postage stamp sized lot? Then this home in the desirable Emerald Estates neighborhood might just be the right fit for you. Featuring a newer water heater in '22, furnace in'20, central a/c in '16, roof in '14 and kitchen countertops and appliances in '20. Oversize 2 car garage and so much more on a 7,841 square foot lot with deck and tool shed and room to enjoy those warm summer evenings. Close to Pirate Park and miles of THPRD walking/biking trails, Bethany Village shopping, Intel, and Nike with easy access to Portland via Hwy 26. Don't miss it!
